# State Management Rules

## Permitted Paths (Write Access)
- `src/store/**` — all Zustand stores

## Approved Reference Paths (Read-Only)
- `src/data/widgetTemplates.json`
- `src/data/devices.json`
- `src/engine/codegen/index.js` (for output interface reference)

## Restricted Paths
- All files in `src/pages/**`
- All files in `src/components/**`
- All files in `src/engine/**`

## Core Data Schema Guidelines
- Keep stores decoupled. Do not mix canvas widget states with device pin configurations.
- Use `immer` (or recursive copy utilities) to guarantee immutable updates for nested stores.
- Do not store React components inside the Zustand store; store only serialized data structures.
- Implement selective and debounced state snapshot capturing to prevent memory leak issues on undo/redo actions.
